HEADWORD: Gaslight
<hw>Gas"light`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
light yielded by the combustion of illuminating gas.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A gas jet or burner.</def>⟦br⟧
